/JDocFile/TYDV/111%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c490%2c20220629%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TYDV,111,訴,490,20220629,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"490","JDATE":"20220629","JTITLE":"清償借款"}